dc_title_s: Map of Maumee River (lower portion) and Tenmile Creek Basins showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water, from data compiled by Lawrence R. Brunstetter.|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|Scale bar lower left corner.|Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Maumee River (lower portion) and Tenmile Creek Basins and the quality of underground water.
